Package seedu.address.logic.commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddCommand
    Represents the command to add an activity into the calendar of NOVA.
    AddTaskCommand
    Represents the command to add a task into the calendar of NOVA.
    Command
    Represents a command with hidden internal logic and the ability to be executed.
    CommandResult
    Represents the result of a command execution.
    CompleteTaskCommand
    Represents the command to mark a specified task as completed.
    DeleteCommand
    Represents the command to delete an activity from the calendar in NOVA.
    DeleteTaskCommand
    Represents the command to delete a task from the calendar of NOVA.
    ExitCommand
    Represents the command to terminate the program.
    HelpCommand
    Represents the command to format full help instructions for every command for display.
    ResetCommand
    Represents the command to reset the calendar to a clean slate and adjust the period of the calendar to start on the user specified start date.
    ViewCommand
    Represents the command to Views all activities of a date.
